ml": "<p>Found a crash while going through the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://gazebosim.org/tutorials/?tut=system_plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">system_gui</a> tutorial.</p>\n<p>In <code>GuiIface.cc</code>'s <code>gui::run()</code> function, the system plugin is initialized in <code>setupClient()</code> which happens before the gui is actually loaded, so the user camera is still null and causes a crash</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-07-11T22:50:01.761655+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:45:08.058551+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1227}